explanation.summary: Kt qu in tm  cho thy nhp tim ca bn chm hn mc bnh thng, nhng cc tn hiu in khc ca tim vn n nh.
explanation.details: Hnh nh sng in tim cho thy nhp tim ca bn u nhng chm. C th, nhp tim hin ti l 57.51 ln/pht, thp hn ngng bnh thng (60-100 ln/pht). Tuy nhin, thi gian dn truyn in tim qua cc bung di ca tim (QRS 0.104s) vn trong gii hn an ton (0.08 - 0.12s), cho thy tim vn co bp hiu qu v khng c du hiu tc nghn ng dn truyn in. Bin  sng R l 6.41 mV, v kh nng bin thin nhp tim (HRV) l 36.891 ms, u l cc ch s bnh thng, phn nh kh nng iu chnh nhp tim tt ca c th.
explanation.recommendations: Nu bn khng c bt k triu chng no nh chng mt, mt mi qu mc, kh th hay ngt xu, nhp tim chm c th l bnh thng, c bit nu bn l vn ng vin hoc ang dng mt s loi thuc. Hy tip tc theo di sc khe v trnh cc hot ng gng sc qu mc nu bn cm thy khng khe.
explanation.next_steps: Nu bn c bt k triu chng kh chu no lin quan n nhp tim chm hoc tnh trng ny ko di, bn nn tham kho  kin bc s chuyn khoa tim mch  c nh gi k hn v xc nh nguyn nhn.
